metadata.name: RTFKT LuxPod
metadata.description:
RTFKT Exo Pod


As part of the Exodus, clones are moving from planet 42 Draconis b.

Formed in part from the materials of 2 Space Pods and 2 Loot Pods, a new Exo Pod was built for utility to be transported within the ExoPod Explorer Class ship for the journey ahead.

With its comfy and welcoming Exo Pod interior, the ExoPod Explorer Class ship is the social hub of the Clone X Exodus fleet.

Digital Collectible terms and conditions apply, see https://rtfkt.com/legal-2D

An immersive interior Exo Pod experience is available at https://oncyber.io with OnCyber enabling Exo Pod 3D customization and exploration, alone or with friends.
